00:01:03,859 --> 00:01:08,030
So the way this game plays is kind of like any other tower defense game out there.

12
00:01:08,030 --> 00:01:15,030
You build towers to stop waves of creeps from taking something that is yours, and what is yours are these five gems.

13
00:01:15,030 --> 00:01:21,340
If all five of those leave, you lose the game. It's pretty standard when it comes to tower defense,

14
00:01:21,340 --> 00:01:26,340
you just build, you kill, and that's it. But, but, but, but, but, there's a major but here.

15
00:01:26,340 --> 00:01:32,340
After every round, you're going to get experience points, and this is something I never see tower defense games do,

16
00:01:32,340 --> 00:01:38,510
which gives me this urge to play it a million times. There are skill points in this game,

17
00:01:38,510 --> 00:01:43,689
and there are skilled trees in this game. You level up. You actually level up in this game,

18
00:01:43,689 --> 00:01:47,689
and then you use the points to make your towers better in the three various trees.

19
00:01:47,689 --> 00:01:53,689
Each tree is totally different. You can play through this game three times, totally,

20
00:01:53,689 --> 00:01:59,689
and get a different experience each time you play. And the simplicity of it all will really take you by surprise.

21
00:01:59,689 --> 00:02:06,859
There's only three towers in this entire game. You don't get 50 towers or 12 different towers to choose from.

22
00:02:06,859 --> 00:02:11,860
There's only three, and each one corresponds to a different skill tree.

23
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:18,300
But there is a twist. You can only build these towers on the corresponding land that they are allowed.

24
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:21,300
For instance, you can only build the green towers on the green grass.

25
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:27,300
You can only build the crypt towers on the snow, and the red towers can only go on the red clay.

26
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:31,300
So you have to do a lot of strategy, and you have to really figure out what towers you're going to use,

27
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:36,659
and they have to work in tandem, which brings me to the difficulty of this game.

28
00:02:36,659 --> 00:02:41,840
Once you get past the first five to ten levels, you'll start losing gems more often than not,

29
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:44,840
and you might have to go back and rework your build.

30
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:50,080
I can't believe I'm actually saying the word build in a tower defense game, but that is the honest-to-god truth.

31
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:54,080
You have to have a good build, and you have to really work to your play style.

32
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:58,080
Maybe you don't like the slow, slug tower of the crypt.

33
00:02:58,080 --> 00:03:01,080
