34
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:05,080
And maybe you want to go maybe in between. You want to have the orc tower and the crypt tower.

35
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,080
There's a lot to it.

36
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:10,449
One thing I did not talk about yet are the mana abilities in this game.

37
00:03:10,449 --> 00:03:12,449
There are three, just like there are three towers.

38
00:03:12,449 --> 00:03:16,449
You generate mana as you play, and you can pick one of these three moves.

39
00:03:16,449 --> 00:03:20,449
One of them is chopping down trees to put more towers down, which is incredibly useful.

40
00:03:20,449 --> 00:03:23,449
The second one is a burn move, so to speak.

41
00:03:23,449 --> 00:03:27,449
It's to make all your towers shoot 200% faster for a small duration.

42
00:03:27,449 --> 00:03:32,750
